commit.message:
Add `Mtime.Span.{is_shorter,is_longer}.

These are analogous to `Mtime.{is_earlier,is_later}`: they make the
comparisons very obvious.

Closes #49.
Fix MacOS regression introduced by a7bfe32 (#44).
Use the new `js_of_ocaml` META standard to link JavaScript stubs.

Use CLOCK_BOOTTIME on linux and mach_continuous_time on macOS.

Closes #10.

Stop installing the clock interface in mtime.clock.

It's no longer needed. Closes #42.

Change implementation of `Mtime.Span.pp` and drop `pp_float_s`.

Imports the implementation from `B0_std`.
Use Stdlib's unsigned int64 comparison (requires OCaml 4.08).
runtime.js: rework and fix performance.now call (#39).
runtime.js: reinstate old DOMHighResTimeStamp conversion procedure (#39).
Tweak formatting of parent commit and add copyright headers (#39).
